{
  "stem": "7683.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the reason-- the reason I started this business is because an uncle from Selma had a business, and the license was still good, but we could write it over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had written it over to our name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the partner had a-- a location, a store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we came together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He couldn't have the license.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had a license.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we built together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it ended up after so many years that we did very well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it ended up that he swindled us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a hard time to go back to business life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to go, either go-- I wanted to go to America, and Selma wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So Selma won?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She won because we couldn't come into America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have anybody [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- we could easily go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we call it a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What that is is that you work together but you live separate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a kibbutz, you live together and you work together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In a [NON-ENGLISH], what means a village, a partner village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What that means, really, is, you have your own quarters where you live and your children with you and everything, but you go to work with this for the whole community.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- but I couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't stand it from the first day on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I already planned to do something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went every other week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had two days free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every week, you get a day free, so I went every other week and tried to get away from that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after-- I don't remember how many months-- seven, eight, nine months, I found another place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wanted to start to work somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
